! IEEE 33-Bus Radial Distribution Test Feeder
! Source: Baran and Wu (1989), IEEE Transactions on Power Delivery
! Base voltage: 12.66 kV, Base MVA: 100
! Total load: 3715 kW, 2300 kVAr

Clear

New Circuit.IEEE33Bus
~ basekv=12.66
~ pu=1.05
~ phases=3
~ bus1=Bus1
~ Isc3=100000
~ Isc1=100000

! ── LINES ──
