! ── LOADS ──
! Base loads from Baran and Wu (1989), scaled for high-density urban simulation
! EV hub loads injected at Bus18 (end of main feeder, commercial zone)
! Data center loads injected at Bus33 (end of lateral, industrial zone)
! Background loads at remaining buses represent existing urban demand

New Load.Load2  phases=3 bus1=Bus2  kv=12.66 kW=20  kvar=12  model=1
New Load.Load3  phases=3 bus1=Bus3  kv=12.66 kW=18  kvar=8  model=1
